{"id":"guide/understanding-angular-overview","title":"理解 Angular","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"understanding-angular\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dnkbhowdx9bqwgst44lrsfdr4\">理解 Angular<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-angular-overview#understanding-angular\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"n6uikbmi1cmykcii80c7wn2h\">要了解 Angular 框架的功能，你需要了解以下内容：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c7vzzlnsersqq3lvejga81lr\">组件</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7ghjndclzhjnvo01a3d1ff3nc\">模板</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9uaad125h3hufxqa64leub0r9\">指令</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ev35fdpq1f46jvj853hmazgoj\">依赖注入</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b1rjvpqh0z3l1tx9d9q57qi6v\">本节中的主题解释了这些功能和概念，以及如何使用它们。</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e44b21uig1fakj5vcfuvz1bdu\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-angular-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8ihh39r3owciq2m2ntn0tmovp\">要充分利用这些开发人员指南，你应该查看以下主题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"94rl86q2f2b7rhc21ygp7pv27\"><a href=\"guide/what-is-angular\" title=\"What is Angular\\? | Angular\">什么是 Angular</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"duipjg6v9boyuudh8vdct6z2m\"><a href=\"start\" title=\"Getting started with Angular | Angular\">入门教程</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-angular-basics\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e1cbz2xzmflcabedozz27cyde\">了解 Angular 基础知识<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-angular-overview#learn-about-angular-basics\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n  <a href=\"guide/component-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Components\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c7vzzlnsersqq3lvejga81lr\">组件</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aie696gno4rvxn8xnw35e3951\">学习 Angular 组件。组件是 Angular 开发中的关键构造块。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c7vzzlnsersqq3lvejga81lr\">组件</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/template-syntax\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Templates\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7ghjndclzhjnvo01a3d1ff3nc\">模板</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"29zsr163fz5gbebgyt2i3og6e\">学习如何构建 Angular 模板。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7ghjndclzhjnvo01a3d1ff3nc\">模板</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/built-in-directives\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Directives\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9uaad125h3hufxqa64leub0r9\">指令</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bf88knhmp77jgv5ytsem2cjb3\">学习 Angular 指令。指令是一个类，用于在 Angular 应用中为元素添加额外的行为。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9uaad125h3hufxqa64leub0r9\">指令</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/dependency-injection\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Dependency injection\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ev35fdpq1f46jvj853hmazgoj\">依赖注入</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dhwm4vqnureihaixu7cncbvax\">了解依赖注入。依赖注入是Angular用来创建和提供类需要执行特定功能的服务或对象的模式。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ev35fdpq1f46jvj853hmazgoj\">依赖注入</p>\n  </a>\n  <!-- <a href=\"guide/rendering-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular service worker developer guide\">\n    <section>Rendering</section>\n    <p>Learn how about server-side rendering and pre-rendering using Angular Universal.</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\">Angular Universal</p>\n  </a> -->\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间：Mon Feb 28 2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/developer-guide-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/built-in-directives\n - guide/component-overview\n - guide/dependency-injection\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/understanding-angular-overview#learn-about-angular-basics\n - guide/understanding-angular-overview#prerequisites\n - guide/understanding-angular-overview#understanding-angular\n - guide/what-is-angular\n - start\n-->"}